name: Protogen Technologies
overview:
Protogen is an Australian firm that predominantly services the Sydney and Brisbane market in the areas of Business Intelligence, Collaboration, Application and Database Outsourcing, Data Warehousing and Built to Order systems.

Our passion is software and how it can be used to help make businesses more successful and profitable. We help automate workflows, speed up application performance and get the most out of existing systems and data.

Every business is unique, with customised processes that help sell your products, service customers and manage employees. Inevitably, businesses end up with a wide range of technology tools, with most of them working independently. These technology silos are generally inefficient and increase workloads for your team.

Working closely with your management team, we will architect an innovative, intelligent technology solution. One designed specifically to help you achieve your revenue growth, and efficiency improvement targets.

Starting with our knowledge base of proven designs, we are able to significantly reduce the risk, time, and costs involved with software deployment and integration.

Our approach is hands-on, and collaborative. Our aim is to ensure a smooth project deployment, with the maximum skills and knowledge transfer.

This approach ensures that your team becomes both empowered, and self sufficient. When you need help, we are able to proactively monitor, maintain, and support your key business applications and databases.
